今日天气：$alignc${weather http://weather.noaa.gov/pub/data/observations/metar/stations/  ZGNN temperature  (30)}°C$alignr ${weather http://weather.noaa.gov/pub/data/observations/metar/stations/ ZGNN cloud_cover  (30)}
